OL,3,CWho is Wes Streeting?
OL,5,FHaving been an MP for 11 years and a
OL,6,Fcabinet minister for two, Wes
OL,7,FStreeting has made no secret of his
OL,8,Fambitions to become prime minister.
OL,10,FWhile his rapid ascent - from a
OL,11,Fchildhood of poverty to high office -
OL,12,Fhas attracted admiration from some,
OL,13,Fhis unashamed ambition has also
OL,14,Fbrought criticism.
OL,16,FSo who is Wes Streeting, how did he
OL,17,Fget to where he is, and what is his
OL,18,Frecord so far?
OL,20,FWhat is his background?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
