OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778789156
OL,3,CWho is Wes Streeting?
OL,5,F"I'm not your typical politician,"
OL,6,Fsays Streeting on his Labour Party
OL,7,Fwebsite page.
OL,9,F"I come from a working class family in
OL,10,FTower Hamlets. I funded myself through
OL,11,Fcollege and university with retail
OL,12,Fjobs and I spent my professional
OL,13,Fcareer working outside politics in the
OL,14,Fvoluntary sector."
OL,16,FThat working class family included a
OL,17,Fgrandfather who spent time in prison
OL,18,Fand unmarried teenage parents who
OL,19,Fstruggled to pay the bills.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
