OL,3,CWho is Wes Streeting?
OL,5,FYet he went on to become the first
OL,6,Fperson in his family to graduate from
OL,7,Funiversity.
OL,9,FHe credits this in part to his mother,
OL,10,Fwho was determined he should be
OL,11,Fsurrounded by books and his father,
OL,12,Fwho also pushed him do well at school
OL,13,Fand go on to university.
OL,15,FThat opportunity came when one of his
OL,16,Fteachers spotted his potential and
OL,17,Fsuggested he should apply to
OL,18,FWestminster City School ` a high-
OL,19,Fperforming state academy from where he
OL,20,Fwon a place to read history at Selwyn
OL,21,FCollege, Cambridge.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
