OL,3,CWho is Wes Streeting?
OL,5,FStreeting details this path in his
OL,6,Fmemoir, which was published in 2023.
OL,8,FAccording to the sleeve notes: "Wes
OL,9,FStreeting might have ended up in
OL,10,Fprison rather than in parliament. His
OL,11,Fmaternal grandfather Bill, an
OL,12,Funsuccessful armed robber, spent time
OL,13,Fbehind bars, as did his grandmother,
OL,14,Fwho was also a political campaigner."
OL,16,FIn his political life, Streeting often
OL,17,Frefers to his own experience growing
OL,18,Fup in poverty. Last year, he told ITV
OL,19,FNews, he is "a product of what happens
OL,20,Fwhen the state does things right".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
