OL,3,CWho is Wes Streeting?
OL,5,F"I wouldn't be sat here today without
OL,6,Fthe benefits my mum got," he said.
OL,8,FWhat did he do before entering
OL,9,Fparliament?
OL,11,FStreeting's first jobs were in the
OL,12,Fpublic and charity sectors, including
OL,13,Fa term as president of the National
OL,14,FUnion of Students from 2008 to 2010.
OL,16,FHe also held roles at charities
OL,17,Ffocused on tackling inequality and
OL,18,Feducational disadvantage, including
OL,19,FThe Helena Kennedy Foundation.
OL,26,@mD@AOUnD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
