OL,3,CWho is Wes Streeting?
OL,5,FStreeting, who came out as gay at
OL,6,Funiversity, also served as head of
OL,7,Feducation at the LGBT rights charity
OL,8,FStonewall, where he led a campaign to
OL,9,Ftackle homophobia in schools.
OL,11,FIn 2010, after a stint working for the
OL,12,FBlairite think tank, Progress, he won
OL,13,Fa seat on Redbridge Council in east
OL,14,FLondon, going to serve as the
OL,15,Fborough's deputy leader and cabinet
OL,16,Fmember for health and wellbeing.
OL,18,FWhat about his parliamentary career?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
