OL,3,CWho is Wes Streeting?
OL,5,FStreeting was elected to Parliament as
OL,6,FMP for Ilford North in the 2015
OL,7,Fgeneral election, bucking the trend
OL,8,Fwith the largest swing from the
OL,9,FConservatives to Labour in the country.
OL,11,FAt Westminster, he quickly caught the
OL,12,Feye, even among political opponents,
OL,13,Fwith then Chancellor George Osborne
OL,14,Fpicking him out as a future star.
OL,16,FWhen Jeremy Corbyn was elected as
OL,17,Fleader of the Labour Party, Streeting
OL,18,Fwas one of his most outspoken critics
OL,19,Fon the party's backbenches, lambasting
OL,20,Fhis failure to tackle antisemitism
OL,21,Fwithin its ranks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
