OL,3,CWho is Wes Streeting?
OL,5,FHe remained a back-bencher under
OL,6,FCorbyn, but was promoted to shadow
OL,7,Fminister for schools when Keir Starmer
OL,8,Ftook over in 2020.
OL,10,FThis was the start of his rapid rise
OL,11,Fthrough the ranks of front bench
OL,12,Fpositions.
OL,14,FIn the May 2021 shadow cabinet
OL,15,Freshuffle, he became Shadow Secretary
OL,16,Fof State for Child Poverty. He was
OL,17,Fpromoted again in November 2021, to
OL,18,Fthe post of Shadow Health Secretary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
