OL,3,CWho is Wes Streeting?
OL,5,FHis progress was briefly interrupted
OL,6,Fwhen he announced he was stepping back
OL,7,Ffrom frontline politics after being
OL,8,Fdiagnosed with kidney cancer, but
OL,9,Fwithin four months he was back after a
OL,10,Fsuccessful operation to remove one of
OL,11,Fhis kidneys.
OL,13,FWhen Starmer faced demands to resign
OL,14,Fover claims he broke Covid lockdown
OL,15,Frules, Streeting rode to his leader's
OL,16,Fdefence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
