OL,3,CWho is Wes Streeting?
OL,5,FHis loyalty was rewarded. When Labour
OL,6,Fwon the general election in 2024,
OL,7,FStarmer made Streeting Health
OL,8,FSecretary, a position he held until
OL,9,Fhis resignation on Thursday.
OL,11,FHighlights and low points of his
OL,12,Fcabinet career?
OL,14,FStreeting's association with disgraced
OL,15,Fpeer Peter Mandelson has been regarded
OL,16,Fby some in Westminster as a possible
OL,17,Fhurdle to becoming Labour leader.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
