OL,3,CWho is Wes Streeting?
OL,5,FIn February, Streeting shared a
OL,6,Ftranscript of messages between himself
OL,7,Fand the former Labour grandee as he
OL,8,Fsought to distance himself from the
OL,9,Fpeer.
OL,11,FThe messages were due to be published
OL,12,Fwith a tranche of other documents
OL,13,Frelating to Mandelson's appointment as
OL,14,Fambassador to the US.
OL,16,FAmong the exchanges were concerns
OL,17,Fexpressed by Mr Streeting that the
OL,18,Fgovernment had "no growth strategy"
OL,19,Fand that he would be "toast" at the
OL,20,Fnext general election.
