OL,3,CWho is Wes Streeting?
OL,5,FOn the other hand, Streeting says he
OL,6,Fhas delivered on the "ambitious
OL,7,Ftargets" that Starmer set for him when
OL,8,Fhe became Health Secretary.
OL,10,FIn his resignation letter, which
OL,11,Fcoincided with new waiting time
OL,12,Ffigures, he said: "Today's figures
OL,13,Fconfirm that we surpassed our waiting
OL,14,Ftimes target despite strikes, and that
OL,15,Fwaiting lists fell by 110,000 in March
OL,16,F- the biggest monthly drop outside of
OL,17,FCovid since 2008 - meaning that we are
OL,18,Fon track to achieve the fastest
OL,19,Fimprovement in NHS waiting times in
OL,20,Fhistory."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
