OL,3,CWho is Wes Streeting?
OL,5,FWhich wing of the Labour Party is he
OL,6,Faligned with?
OL,8,FA fluent and effective communicator,
OL,9,FStreeting is seen as a champion of the
OL,10,Fright wing of the Labour Party.
OL,12,FHe is openly patriotic and strong on
OL,13,Flaw and order.
OL,15,FHe has been compared to Tony Blair,
OL,16,Falthough he rejects the label
OL,17,F"Blairite" as too divisive.
